From lli Lori Iannamico Subject Re Too Many Europeans in NHL In article Richard John Rauser writes Ten years ago the number of Europeans in the NHL was roughly a quarter of what it is Going into the season the numbers of Euros on NHL teams have escalated to the following stats Canadians Americans Europeans Xenophobic trash I'm all for the creation of a European Hockey League and let the Bures and Selannes of the world play on their own I just don't want them on If you're going to go to those extremes I guess you'd better start Because unless you're a Native North American this isn't your continent Lori